			title: "The Coin of the Realm"
			x: 0.0d
			y: 0.0d
		}
		{
			dependencies: ["5E5E000000000001"]
			description: ["The Coin Mint converts raw material into money and back again: feed it ingots and it stamps coins of the matching tier. This is how new currency enters the economy — your mining trips and GT casting lines can literally print money. The mint works in reverse as well, melting surplus coins back into usable metal. Set one up early; a stack of iron you were going to smelt into plates anyway is also a starting fund."]
			id: "5E5E000000000002"
			rewards: [
				{
