			title: "Minting Money"
			x: -2.5d
			y: 2.5d
		}
		{
			dependencies: ["5E5E000000000002"]
			description: ["The ATM is your bank branch. It exchanges coins up and down the tier chain at the fixed 10:1 rate — a hundred iron coins compress into one emerald coin without losing a copper of value — and it deposits money into your personal bank account, where it cannot be dropped, burned, or looted from your corpse. Traders can be set to pay earnings straight into that account. Carry pocket money; bank everything else."]
			id: "5E5E000000000003"
			rewards: [
				{
					auto: "enabled"
