			title: "Banking at the ATM"
			x: -2.5d
			y: 5.0d
		}
		{
			dependencies: ["5E5E000000000003"]
			description: ["A wallet keeps your coins out of your item inventory and picks up dropped currency automatically. Higher-tier wallets — copper up through netherite — hold more and unlock on-the-go exchanging, so loose iron converts itself into cleaner denominations while you fight. Equip the wallet in its dedicated slot and stop letting coins compete with dungeon loot for backpack space."]
			id: "5E5E000000000004"
