			title: "Waystones"
			x: -5.0d
			y: 2.5d
		}
		{
			dependencies: ["5E5E00000000000C"]
			description: ["The travel network extends beyond the stones themselves. The Warp Stone is a rechargeable personal teleporter to any attuned waystone; warp scrolls are cheap single-use copies for guests and emergencies; return scrolls send you to your nearest bound point. Keep a warp stone on your hotbar during expeditions — the trip home from a dungeon should cost a click, not an hour. Sell warp scrolls at your shop and you are quite literally selling convenience."]
			id: "5E5E00000000000D"
