		{
			dependencies: ["5E5E000000000005"]
			description: ["A shop that looks like a dirt hut sells like one. Macaw's mods carry the structural vocabulary a storefront needs: real doors with glass panes and shop-front styles, windows with shutters and blinds, awning-grade roofs in every wood and shingle, and bridges to carry the market district across the river. Frame the building before you furnish it — a recognizable silhouette is what makes players walk over in the first place."]
			icon: "mcwdoors:oak_glass_door"
