			description: ["A claimed plot, a built storefront, stocked traders on the network, and a waystone at the door. That is not a base anymore — it is an institution. Check this quest off when your shop is open to the public and something has actually sold. The economy of this server is nothing more than the sum of players who decided to build one; you just became part of the infrastructure."]
